  <entry>
    <title>Hexo美化</title>
    <link href="http://faneter.github.io/2020/02/18/Hexo%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/"/>
    <id>http://faneter.github.io/2020/02/18/Hexo%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/</id>
    <published>2020-02-18T02:46:35.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-02-25T05:53:26.459Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Hexo 的美化教程</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="功能性"><a href="#功能性" class="headerlink" title="功能性"></a>功能性</h2><ul><li><h3 id="摘录-excerpt"><a href="#摘录-excerpt" class="headerlink" title="摘录(excerpt)"></a>摘录(excerpt)</h3><p>在主题的<code>_config.yml</code>中<br>找到<code>auto_excerpt</code>,如果没有则创建<br>修改为</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">auto_excerpt:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment"># 自动摘录，开启</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">length:</span> <span class="number">50</span> <span class="comment"># 摘录字数</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>或者在<code>MarkDown</code>文件中添加<code>&lt;!-- more --&gt;</code>在要摘录的文本后面</p></li></ul><h2 id="视觉性"><a href="#视觉性" class="headerlink" title="视觉性"></a>视觉性</h2><h2 id="社交性"><a href="#社交性" class="headerlink" title="社交性"></a>社交性</h2>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;Hexo 的美化教程&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
    
